</head>
<body class = "sk_background page-gutter">

<h3>Who Won?</h3>
<% if @sk_user_total > @sk_cpu_total %>
<div class="sk_winner">
<%= "Your madlib wins!!" %></div>
<% elsif  @sk_cpu_total > @sk_user_total %>
<div class="sk_winner">
<%= "The computer's madlib wins!" %></div>
<% else %>
<% @sk_user_total == @sk_cpu_total %>
<div class="sk_winner">
<%= "It's a tie!" %></div>
<% end %>

<div class="show-container form-margin">
<div class="show-border">

<h2 class="text-pop-up-top">YOU</h2>

<h5>To scare the living daylights out of your chosen victim, </h5>
<p>find a gruesome or <span class="word"><%= Word.find(@sk.word1_id).name %></span> mask or hooded <span class="word"><%= Word.find(@sk.word2_id).name %> </span></p>
<p> to wear along with a fake weapon of choice.</p>
<p>Try a <span class="word"><%= Word.find(@sk.word3_id).name %></span> chainsaw, knife, or weapon of choice.</p>
<p>You jump out as your <span class="word"><%= Word.find(@sk.word4_id).name %></span> victim approaches.</p>
<p>Enjoy the feeling of him/her being thoroughly frightened</p>
<p> at your presence and maybe even <span class="word"><%= Word.find(@sk.word5_id).name %></span> away at full speed.</p>


<div class="sk_total text-pop-up-right" >
<%= @sk_user_total %>
</div>
</div>

<div class="show-border">
<h3 class="text-pop-up-top">COMPUTER</h3>

<h5>To scare the living daylights out of your chosen victim, </h5>
<p>find a gruesome or <span class="word"><%= @cadjectives.sample.name %></span> mask or hooded </p>
<p><span class="word"><%= @cnouns.sample.name %></span> to wear along with a fake weapon of choice.</p>
<p>Try a <span class="word"><%= @cnouns.sample.name %></span> chainsaw, knife, or weapon of choice.</p>
<p>You jump out as your <span class="word"><%= @cadjectives.sample.name %></span> victim approaches.</p>
<p>Enjoy the feeling of him/her being thoroughly frightened</p>
<p> at your presence and maybe even <span class="word"><%=  @cverbs.sample.name %></span> away at full speed.</p>


<div class="sk_total text-pop-up-right">
<%= @sk_cpu_total %>
</div>
</div>
</div>


<div class="start-again-link">
<a><%= button_to 'START AGAIN', home_path, method: :get, class: 'waves-effect waves-light btn-large btn btn-small' %></a>
<!-- <a class="waves-effect waves-light btn-large">Button</a> -->
</div>
</body>
